  "title": "BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>The Business Development Manager plays a key role in expanding Sunstar Cleaning Services Pte. Ltd.’s client base by identifying new business opportunities and developing long-term relationships. This role focuses on driving growth through strategic partnerships and securing contracts in residential, commercial, and F&amp;B sectors.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Specific Responsibilities</p>\n<p>1. Research and identify potential clients and new business opportunities.</p>\n<p>2. Build and maintain strong relationships with stakeholders and decision-makers.</p>\n<p>3. Develop tailored proposals and presentations to meet client needs.</p>\n<p>4. Negotiate terms and close contracts with prospective clients.</p>\n<p>5. Conduct market research to stay updated on industry trends and competitors.</p>\n<p>6. Collaborate with the operations team to align client requirements with service delivery.</p>\n<p>7. Attend networking events to promote company services and expand market reach.</p>\n<p>8. Maintain a pipeline of leads and follow up consistently.</p>\n<p>9. Represent the company in a professional manner to enhance its reputation.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Technical Skills and Competencies</p>\n<p>1. Strong business development and strategic acumen.</p>\n<p>2. Excellent networking and relationship-building skills.</p>\n<p>3. Competence in proposal and contract preparation.</p>\n<p>4. Negotiation and persuasion skills.</p>\n<p>5. Market research and analysis capabilities.</p>\n<p>6. Strong communication and presentation skills.</p>\n<p>7. Ability to identify client needs and offer appropriate solutions.</p>\n<p>8. Strategic planning and business growth orientation.</p>\n<p>9. Professional demeanor with customer-centric focus.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>MID CAREER PROGRAM</p>",
